Package communication

In this package are located all classes used to create udp communication message for Unacloud

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UnaCloudAbstractMessage
    Abstract class to be used by programs to send message to agents
    UnaCloudAbstractResponse
    Abstract class to manage responses from agents
    UnaCloudDataSenderUDP
    Class used to send and receive message using UDP protocol
    UnaCloudMessageUDP
    Used as standard for send message in UDP Protocol
  • Enum Summary

    Enum to represent types of UDP message
